{"tid":559392,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Nintendo Switch 被破解植入《Linux》！黑客宣稱漏洞無法修復","createTime":"2018-02-13T06:43:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T03:55:48.000Z","uid":1886,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"280b88def06286e8b5e25fc6aeebfe5c378269df","tid":559392,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:43:37.000Z","msg":"早在本年 1 月，黑客 fail0verflow 已表示順利破解了 Nintendo Switch，並在其個人 Twitter 上，展示了任天堂 Switch 運行自製文字走馬燈的影片。最近 fail0verflow 又在個人 Twitter 中發放新相片，展示了正運行《Debian》作業系統的 Nintendo Switch，代表 fail0verflow 已順利利用 Nintendo Switch 的系統漏洞，讓《Linux》系統可在任天堂 Switch 上安裝和運行。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2005000/2009940/1018webswitchrunlin01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2005000%2F2009940%2F1018webswitchrunlin01_1024.jpg&h=ad262c42&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2009940/Nintendo%20Switch%20被破解植入《Linux》！黑客宣稱漏洞無法修復\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2009940%2FNintendo%2520Switch%2520%E8%A2%AB%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3%E6%A4%8D%E5%85%A5%E3%80%8ALinux%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%81%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E5%AE%A3%E7%A8%B1%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=0a669262\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2009940/Nintendo%20Switch%20被破解植入《Linux》！黑客宣稱漏洞無法修復</a>"},{"pid":"fa292423fe123bd8885f795c7efbc7de75f435dc","tid":559392,"uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:44:23.000Z","msg":"fail0verflow 表示系統漏洞源自 Nintendo Switch 所使用的 NVIDIA Tegra X1 處理器，屬於「bootrom」形式的程式錯誤，毋須為 Switch 加裝改裝晶片，即可利用該系統漏洞修改 Nintendo Switch 的系統。與此同時，Nintendo 將無法透過更新系統的方法，為現已發售的任天堂 Switch 修補問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。這個發現的最大價值，自然是有可能讓玩家自行為任天堂 Switch 安裝「邪道」系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，運行各款盜版遊戲軟件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。如果 fail0verflow 繼續對 Nintendo Switch 進行破解，尋找出實現 Nintendo Switch 運行盜版遊戲的方法，或會對將來 Nintendo Switch 的遊戲銷情帶來影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"6f7449bbdbed8e3aa577422c171a29d7f794c0ed","tid":559392,"uid":89433,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:45:36.000Z","msg":"R4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdff989bec82f8050339b06f4709c3758a80a93","tid":559392,"uid":107927,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"可以玩翻版即刻大賣"},{"pid":"8c4de65b89313aa47fd75c8d4b044109a04c56a5","tid":559392,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"6bdff989bec82f8050339b06f4709c3758a80a93","tid":559392,"uid":107927,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"可以玩翻版即刻大賣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T10:44:52.000Z","msg":"用 linux"},{"pid":"a07141f0d7d3d549b376513b3b4820ab903c197b","tid":559392,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:01:47.000Z","msg":"nvidia <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d3ea6464bd0adf8c3c9df75f64cfa2863f1af7","tid":559392,"uid":19557,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"6bdff989bec82f8050339b06f4709c3758a80a93","tid":559392,"uid":107927,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"可以玩翻版即刻大賣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:06:13.000Z","msg":"大賣硬件 軟件收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a