aces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ac565f264aecf63f8db4278451b9642036463b","tid":559392,"uid":6366,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:05:27.000Z","msg":"成班啱啱放監？<br />\n講到switch而家唔大賣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定又自己唔買=全世界無人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d51330809ccab7a1a7a1d49fcd33c91acc664e","tid":559392,"uid":133217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"3DS又bootrom<br />\nNS又bootrom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945bfe60d78eecaa6153b6b65b135e857130e101","tid":559392,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe2c54ac499a486ae39e5b69868b839517d8adac","tid":559392,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:29:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">黑客進一步破解任天堂 Switch！變身 Linux 平板機</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黑客 fail0verflow 的破解行動未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為近日再將任天堂 Switch 破解為 Linux 平板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而且在他的 Twitter 帳戶之中，更有操作示範影片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，以及加上 #switchnix hashtag，真正「有片有真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2010000/2014294/20180220_hack_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2010000%2F2014294%2F20180220_hack_01_1024.jpg&h=7eb2b613&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2014294/黑客破解任天堂%20Switch！變身%20Linux%20平板機\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2014294%2F%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82%2520Switch%EF%BC%81%E8%AE%8A%E8%BA%AB%2520Linux%2520%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E6%A9%9F&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a2ddaf39\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2014294/黑客破解任天堂%20Switch！變身%20Linux%20平板機</a>"},{"pid":"6c5f8493cba3a7fec68d2514d4aeb204a7bf07e6","tid":559392,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"從黑客 fail0verflow 的操作示範影片可見，任天堂 Switch 屏幕顯示的，不是遊戲內容，而是 Linux 作業系統，而且也可像 Switch 一樣點按屏幕操作，並能開啟瀏覽器上網、 multi touch 放大縮小文字，甚至開啟虛撿鍵盤打字、執行 GPU 測試都可以，不特別提起也不覺得這並非真正的平板電腦，而是任天堂 Switch。不過在黑客 fail0verflow 的 Twitter 就沒有說明當中是怎樣破解出來，但可以肯定的是，如任天堂再沒有防範措施的話，玩 crack 版 Switch 遊戲的日子應該不遠矣。<br />\n<br />\n有片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/fail0verflow/status/964954316892119040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffail0verflow%2Fstatus%2F964954316892119040&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=661ad43c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffail0verflow%2Fstatus%2F964954316892119040&h=da811ea8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/fail0verflow/status/964954316892119040</a>"},{"pid":"c2dc7ae020c2ad4ba7423aa094fdc745ea4d9f96","tid":559392,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:30:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2010000/2014294/20180220_hack_02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2010000%2F2014294%2F20180220_hack_02_600.jpg&h=58a8bdd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">經破解的 Switch，可像一般 tablet 上網。</span></div>"},{"pid":"95c1a13512700a13525f82d32dfcc79cb63a487a","tid":559392,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2010000/2014294/20180220_hack_03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2010000%2F2014294%2F20180220_hack_03_600.jpg&h=c30df1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">可以做到 multi touch 放大縮小文字。</span></div>"},{"pid":"044f579518e1bb6fa94c452b84b8aef75757ffaa","tid":559392,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:31:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2010000/2014294/20180220_hack_04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2010000%2F2014294%2F20180220_hack_04_600.jpg&h=b7951835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">開啟虛撿鍵盤打字都沒有問題。</span></div>"},{"pid":"501f1047319a07c06ca63b0741086f1fab4bd347","tid":559392,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:32:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2010000/2014294/20180220_hack_05_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2010000%2F2014294%2F20180220_hack_05_600.jpg&h=2c30545a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> 最勁